                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010114-76-off418 t18010114-76-cd419"></join>, two coats, value 25s. two waistcoats, value 12s. a pair of breeches, value 10s. and a pair of silver sleeve-buttons, value 1s. 6d. the property of 
                     
